version_description:
Towerlands 1.9.1 <br>
<br>In this version:
<br>- Added new combat modules for towers: Magicians, Arcane cannon, Dragon wrath, Shrapnel;
<br>- And also new types of towers: Dragon flame, Totem summoner, Rocky Guard, Magical castle;
<br>- Now PVP-notifications are more compact. You can now turn them off in settings;<br>- Visual fixes;
<br>- Bug fixes.

Towerlands 1.10.2
<br>
<br>In this version:
<br>- Added 5 new units;
<br>- Changed the appearance of the Tower screen. Now it is easier to change the view of the Tower;
<br>- Added a global chat. Communicate with players all over the world or only from your region;
<br>- The Map has been changed.  Now not conquered castles are hidden in the fog. By capturing them you will illuminate the whole map;
<br>- Localization fixes;
<br>- Balance corrections;
<br>- Visual improvements;
<br>- Bug fixes.

Towerlands 1.12 "Winter Battles"
<br>
<br>In this version:
<br>- The new winter event! Fight other players and receive Crowns and Stones for each victory. Battle rewards can be exchanged for valuable prizes;
<br>- Now, each view ad fills up a special scale. Build up your rewards for more gifts!
<br>- Chat in clan chat with stickers!
<br>- Added 4 new units: Ice Master, Exploding, Demon hunter, Builder;
<br>- As well as 3 new towers: Predatory hedge, Hand of the Golem, Ent. And one new module: Stronghold;
<br>- Some units dressed up in festive costumes!
<br>- Bug fixes and game optimizations.

Towerlands 1.14 
<br>
<br>In this version:
<br>- Added Quests! Complete quests, receive Keys, and unlock epic reward chests;
<br>- Badges for player and clan appeared. Get Achievements for playing the game!
<br>- Added Leaderboards to the PvP Event. Now you can find out who's the strongest fighter!
<br>- Clan Upgrades can now be reset and redistributed;
<br>- Added 1000 new enemy waves!
<br>- "Time x2" and "Autobattle" rewards are now replaceable for players with a subscription;
<br>- Added new levels of improvements to the Library;
<br>- Fixed wave health display if it has the necromancer boss that summons skeletons;
<br>- Improved optimization for weak phones;
<br>- Fixed sounds of knights' attacks;
<br>- Visual fixes.
